										<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed...</p>
									</a>
								</li>
								<li>
									<a href="#">
										<img src="~/PersonelSayfasi/vendors/images/photo4.jpg" alt="">
										<h3>Renee I. Hansen</h3>
										<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed...</p>
									</a>
								</li>
								<li>
									<a href="#">
										<img src="~/PersonelSayfasi/vendors/images/img.jpg" alt="">
